  "text": "We consider the query Q which is defined as query Q with the ACs dropped and the views V 1 and V 2 which are the two views again without the ACs in their definition. In this case the rewriting of Q using V does not contain redundant subgoals. Still, it is not a containment minimal rewriting [CITATION_1] , i.e. there is another equivalent rewriting of Q using V which is the following:",
